not all the request might come in single recv on the socket. the buffer is for the headers only, if buffer is fully parsed (lastProcessedByte becomes >= headersBufferEndPos) and end of the headers is not found (\r\n\r\n), then return -1. when the headers are parsed and body should be received, set state to "AwaitingBody" and bodyExpectedLength to respective bytes count, that's the end of the request parsing 
